…Those who target the Kingstone
are my enemies as well.
That is all.{END}

…That sword… the Satan Saber…
proof of the Creation King.
…So you are the other Century King…{END}

You are Jagan… no,
the Century King from 50,000 years ago!
…That body… where did it come from!?{END}

…It is impossible
for you to stop me…
Perish.{END}
